Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:15.51,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I don't know what I should do now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.75,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}With every strength I can take to break enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.51,0:01:35.36,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}絶縁體のような表情で　抵抗を嫌う口実を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.43,0:01:39.61,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}共振拒む理由なんて　単純すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:53.66,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Why don't you ever try
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:57.21,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I won't let you down come along with me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.21,0:01:59.98,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Taking back my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.68,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Why don't you ever try
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:07.96,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}確信はその手にある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:13.25,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm waiting for till the break of dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:15.73,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Taking back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:18.98,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}錆付いた意志でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:21.36,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Just change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:25.03,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}革命に似た Calling back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:27.27,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Tell me what's wrong with the society
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:29.26,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}that everybody is saying OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:33.06,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Low resistance of high zest inner cells
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:35.10,opjp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Rebuild the coil there is no lie
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:15.51,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我现在该做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.75,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}明明有了一切击败敌人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.51,0:01:35.36,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你露出绝缘体般的表情 说着不愿抵抗的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.43,0:01:39.61,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但拒绝共振的理由 却太过单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:53.66,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为何不尝试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:57.21,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不会让你失望 随我前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.21,0:01:59.98,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我要夺回我的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:04.68,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为何不尝试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:07.96,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}信心就在你的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:13.25,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我会等待 直到黎明破晓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:15.73,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}夺回一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:18.98,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即便意志已然锈蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:21.36,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只是改变这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:25.03,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}革命一般 回收一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:27.27,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个社会究竟怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.27,0:02:29.26,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}大家为何习以为常？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:33.06,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}高功率内细胞的低电阻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:35.10,opch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}重建构线圈 让一切谎言烟消云散
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.39,0:22:47.79,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,灰色の街に一粒の雨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:53.79,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,息を止めた記憶の囚われ人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:56.41,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,瞼に焼き付く烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:59.21,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,脆いナイフ振り回し
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:03.17,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,崩れ落ちた未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.42,0:23:09.25,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとスローに見える世界に閉じ込められ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:15.11,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,いつの間にか自分すら憎んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:20.22,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,禁断の果実に手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:27.47,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,名前のない細胞が叫ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.16,0:23:33.36,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,閃光よ　走り出せ　幻を暴くようにと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:38.70,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,完璧を求める「異常」な時代に Siren
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:43.93,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,胸の奥　鳴り響く　確かな疑惑の Discord
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:49.07,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,諸刃の感情　自分を貫く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:51.97,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,「始まりと終わり」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:24:01.48,edjp,,0000,0000,0000,,その境界線上で1つの可能性　切り開け
Comment: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.39,0:22:47.79,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,落入灰暗街道的一粒雨滴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:53.79,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,深陷记忆牢笼的人不禁止住呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:56.41,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睑上的烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:59.21,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,挥动脆弱的匕首
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:03.17,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,未来已是一片废墟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.42,0:23:09.25,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,闷在缓慢流逝的封闭世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:15.11,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉连自我都变得可憎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:20.22,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,向禁断之果伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:27.47,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,无名的细胞吶喊道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.16,0:23:33.36,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,闪光啊 奔跑吧 让一切虚幻现於光天化日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:38.70,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,为苛求完美的「异常」时代拉响警报
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:43.93,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,不断吶喊的心声 诉说着无法调和的疑惑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:49.07,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,双刃的感情刺穿了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:51.97,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,「起始与终结」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:24:01.48,edch,,0000,0000,0000,,将两者之间一丝的可能性 打开
